	<description>
		<![CDATA[
		<div class="overview-header">
			<h2>
			  <small style="display: block;">Responsive Joomla template for portfolio - <strong>JA Jason</strong>.</small>
			</h2>
			<p>The portfolio responsive Joomla template for Joomla 3 & Joomla 2.5 - JA Jason is a revamp for your portfolio. It's a built-in T3 Framework template with Bootstrap 3, RTL Language Layout, K2 Component, and eCommerce ready with Hikashop component.</p> 
			<p>JA Jason shift the focus from yourself onto your products and how to make profit from them. With neat design, and rich typography, JA Jason will be a perfect choice for both your products and designer portfolio.</p>
      <p>With ThemeMagic you will never see yourself wrestling with CSS and PHP codes. For tuning your layout, just use the Layout Configurator.</p>
			<p>JA Jason is a perfect Joomla template for product and designer portfolio; plus, you will be able to make money from the built-in store.</p>
			</div>
		]]>
	</description>
